cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Naga"
authors:
  - name: "enchanter-ai"
abstract: >
  Observes an existing artifact's structural and stylistic fingerprint and
  generates new artifacts that match the observed shape, vocabulary, and
  naming idiom. Pattern replication orthogonal to prompt engineering from
  scratch, structural intelligence, and per-change trust.
version: 0.1.0
date-released: 2026-04-25
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/enchanter-ai/naga"
keywords:
  - claude-code
  - pattern-replication
  - tree-edit-distance
  - tfidf
  - cosine-similarity
  - levenshtein
